title: Ep. - 268 - JENNIFER SEY, FORMER GYMNAST AND PRODUCER OF ATHLETE A
description:
Jennifer Sey is an author, business executive and former gymnast. She began competing in gymnastics at the age of six and went on to become a seven-time member of the United States national team.

She is the author of "Chalked Up: My Life in Elite Gymnastics" and a producer for Athlete A, the Netflix documentary, which recounts the shocking USA Gymnastics sex abuse scandal, in which more than 500 former patients of sports doctor Larry Nassar reported having been molested by over a period of several decades.
